ait for a convenient pause in my literary labors to sort things out. In the meantime please tell me more about the new law you mention and what and how exactly would it benefit my estate if I "deposited at" rather than "gave to" the Library more of my papers.

Best wishes.





Sincerely yours,

Vladimir Nabokov





